Package: rsgl
Title: An Implementation of the SGL Graphics Language
Version: 0.1.0
Authors@R:
    person(
        "Jon", "Chapman", , "jochapjo@icloud.com",
        role = c("aut", "cre")
    )
Description: Parses and executes SGL (Structured Graphics Language) statements
    against 'DuckDB' databases to produce 'ggplot2' visualizations. SGL is a
    declarative language for generating statistical graphics from relational
    data. See Chapman (2025) <doi:10.48550/arXiv.2505.14690> for the language
    specification.
License: MIT + file LICENSE
URL: https://github.com/sgl-projects/rsgl
